abstract: Comedy videos spoofing of “The Social Network,” the upcoming Hollywood retelling of the origins of Facebook, are circulating around the Web.
snippet: Comedy videos spoofing of “The Social Network,” the upcoming Hollywood retelling of the origins of Facebook, are circulating around the Web.
lead_paragraph: It remains to be seen whether or not “The Social Network,” the highly fictionalized retelling of the origins of Facebook, will be a box-office hit.
